{"id": 3137, "genre": 1000, "title": "你最想吐槽哪种“互联网野生文学”？", "description": "小学语文课堂开课啦。（题图来自：iStock ©️undrey ）", "record_count": 67169, "comment_count": 161, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/202001252119564h3n8RByGM57ObN9.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2020-01-25T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6214, "title": "你最想吐槽哪种“互联网野生文学”？", "content": "你最想吐槽哪种“互联网野生文学”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 352093, "content": "仿写，隔一段时间就开始集体模拟最近热门文体／段子", "image": "img/option/option/20200125221822yg8WxUsmRT24BY6t.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 352094, "content": "双关，以各种谐音梗为代表：“鼠你有钱”", "image": "img/option/option/202001252223010cFRbQGy59MVs62A.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 352095, "content": "造词，给产品起代号“黑绷带／前男友面膜”", "image": "img/option/option/20200125222558fdwIeiOoHNRXtSnC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 352096, "content": "反问，表达观点时一句话一个问号", "image": "img/option/option/202001252227223Z0vqFI9HSmdywGW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 352097, "content": "拟人，管冠状病毒叫“阿冠”…", "image": "img/option/option/20200125223419MQ2scphV08f9XEDZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 352098, "content": "造句，“____不易，且行且珍惜。”", "image": "img/option/option/20200125223613oDtZWdslFSKUq3LH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 352099, "content": "反语，友军“钓鱼”行为，多靠狗头来识别", "image": "img/option/option/20200125224125bfqT6E2AZHkBUn3c.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 352100, "content": "反复，人类本质是复读机", "image": "img/option/option/20200125223815ZD2GAxEpbN3S9MO1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 352101, "content": "都不反感／我还有其他语文素材", "image": "img/option/option/20200125224246q241ZQzI35oeuDTr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}